Here is a clean, production-ready implementation of **Fix Memory Leak in event listeners (variant 14)** in Debugging.

### Explanation
Cleans up listeners in components to release references on destroy. Specifically, this handles variant case 14.

### Implementation
```python
class EventSourceV14 {
  constructor() {
    this.listeners = [];
  }
  subscribe(fn) {
    this.listeners.push(fn);
    return () => {
      this.listeners = this.listeners.filter(l => l !== fn);
    };
  }
}
```

